.SH subst
.PP
Associates a path with a drive letter.
If used without parameters, \f[B]subst\f[R] displays the names of the
virtual drives in effect.
.SS Syntax
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
subst [<drive1>: [<drive2>:]<path>]
subst <drive1>: /d
\f[R]
.fi
.SS Parameters
.PP
